map homeabout usour businessour teaminvestor relations apollo is a leading global alternative investment manager we are contrarian valueoriented investors in private equity credit and real estate we focus our investments in areas where we can capitalize upon our integrated platform we have applied this investment philosophy over our year history deploying capital across the balance sheet of industry leading businesses and seeking to create value for our investors throughout economic cycles   private equity we have a demonstrated ability to adapt quickly to changing market environments our private equity business is a key component of our investment activities credit we seek to participate in high margin credit businesses where our industry expertise can be used to generate attractive investment returns real estate we seek to produce compelling riskadjusted returns across a broad range of real estate debt and equity investments publicly listed funds managed by apollo click publicly listed funds managed by apollo to learn more about our publicly listed investment vehicles  apollo global management llc  all rights reserved apollo global management ® is a registered trademark of apollo privacy policyterms of useforward looking statements careers you are now leaving our website apollo global management llc and its subsidiaries assume no responsibility for information or statements you may encounter on the internet outside our website thank you for visiting wwwagmcom click here to proceed to the next page homelp logincontact ussitemap homeabout usour businessour teaminvestor relations about us  careers overview citizenship locations careers about our people we are committed to identifying developing valuing and retaining high performing individuals who work well with our broader team and who are capable of delivering exceptional results in their area of expertise apollo has an entrepreneurial environment that is intellectually stimulating highly focused on creating positi